<view class="container">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">点击式生成招募海报</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">不用写文案，不用会设计。几次点击，30 秒产出专业海报。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">选择场景</view>

  <view class="scene-list">
    <view
      class="scene-item"
      wx:for="{{scenes}}"
      wx:key="id"
      bindtap="onPickScene"
      data-id="{{item.id}}"
    >
      <view class="scene-name">{{item.name}}</view>
      <view class="scene-subtitle">{{item.subtitle}}</view>
      <view class="scene-desc">{{item.description}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    当前为 MVP 骨架。完整问答 flow 与模板生成仍在开发中，请先在 H5 端体验。
  </view>
</view>
